{
  "info": {
    "name": "Casino Online API",
    "description": "Colección completa de la API REST del Casino en Línea.\n\n## Setup rápido\n1. Importa este archivo en Postman\n2. Importa también el archivo `casino-env.postman_environment.json`\n3. Selecciona el environment **Casino Local** en la esquina superior derecha\n4. Ejecuta **Auth > Login** — el token se guarda automáticamente\n5. Ya puedes usar el resto de requests\n\n## Sockets\nLos eventos de Socket.io están documentados en la carpeta **Sockets (referencia)**.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "casino-online-v1"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Registro, login, sesión y Google OAuth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Manuel\",\n  \"last_name\": \"García\",\n  \"email\": \"manuel@casino.com\",\n  \"day\": 15,\n  \"month\": 3,\n  \"year\": 2000,\n  \"phone_number\": \"+523311223344\",\n  \"password\": \"mipassword123\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Crea un nuevo usuario. Devuelve JWT en `token`."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (data.token) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('token', data.token);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userId', data.user.id);",
                  "    console.log('✅ Token guardado desde Register');",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login ⚡ (guarda token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{userEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{userPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Inicia sesión. El script de test guarda el JWT en `{{token}}` automáticamente."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Login exitoso', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.environment.set('token', data.token);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('userId', data.user.id);",
                  "  pm.environment.set('userBalance', data.user.bank);",
                  "  console.log('✅ Token guardado automáticamente. Balance:', data.user.bank);",
                  "} else {",
                  "  console.error('❌ Login fallido:', pm.response.json().message);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "POST",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","logout"] },
            "description": "Limpia la cookie httpOnly del servidor."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  pm.environment.unset('token');",
                  "  console.log('Token eliminado del environment');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Me (auth)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","me"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Google OAuth — abrir en navegador",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/google", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","auth","google"] },
            "description": "⚠️ No ejecutar en Postman — abre esta URL en el navegador para iniciar el flujo OAuth.\n\nRequiere GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID y GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET en .env"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
